# Campus Life Planner

A responsive, accessible web app for managing student tasks and events. Built with vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Chosen Theme

**Campus Life Planner** â€” track tasks/events with durations, tags, and due dates.

## Features
- Semantic HTML5 layout with ARIA landmarks
- Mobile-first responsive design (360px, 768px, 1024px)
- Add/edit/delete tasks with inline validation
- Regex-powered live search with safe compiler
- Dashboard with total tasks, duration sum, top tag, and weekly cap logic
- LocalStorage persistence with JSON import/export
- Manual cap setting with ARIA live feedback
- Accessible keyboard navigation and skip-to-content link

## Regex Catalog | Field       | Pattern | Description |
|-------------|---------|-------------|
| Title       | `/^\S(?:.*\S)?$/` | No leading/trailing spaces |
| Duration    | `/^(0|[1-9]\d*)(\.\d{1,2})?$/` | Positive number with up to 2 decimals |
| Due Date    | `/^\d{4}-(0[1-9]|1[0-2])-(0[1-9]|[12]\d|3[01])$/` | Valid YYYY-MM-DD format |
| Tag         | `/^[A-Za-z]+(?:[ -][A-Za-z]+)*$/` | Letters, spaces, hyphens |
| Advanced    | `/\b\d{2}:\d{2}\b/` | Detect time tokens |

## Keyboard Map
 `Tab`: Navigate between inputs and buttons
 `Enter`: Submit form or confirm delete
 `Esc`: Cancel edit (if implemented)
 `Skip link`: Jump to main content

## Accessibility Notes
- Semantic landmarks (`<header>`, `<nav>`, `<main>`, `<section>`, `<footer>`)
- Visible focus styles
- ARIA live regions for cap alerts
- Labels bound to inputs
- Contrast-checked color palette

## Features
- **Add/Edit/Delete Tasks** with persistence in localStorage.  
- **Dashboard/Stats:** Total tasks, total duration, weekly cap remaining, last-7-days trend.  
- **Regex Search & Highlight:** Live search with safe regex compilation.  
- **Validation:** 4+ regex rules including advanced back-reference for duplicate words.  
- **Settings:** Set and persist weekly cap for task durations.  
- **Responsive Design:** Mobile-first, works across three breakpoints (~360px, 768px, 1024px).  
- **Accessibility (a11y):** Keyboard navigation, visible focus, ARIA live regions, labels bound to inputs.

---

## Data Model
Each task is stored as:

```json
{
  "id": "1672531200000",
  "title": "Math homework",
  "dueDate": "2025-10-20",
  "duration": "90",
  "tag": "Study",
  "createdAt": "2025-10-16T10:00:00Z",
  "updatedAt": "2025-10-16T10:00:00Z"
}


